</P>
<P>
   BBA-YANKS (New York) _ Surplus in starting rotation forces
Mendoza to bullpen. By Claire Smith.
</P>
<P>
   HKN-REDWINGS (Washington) _ A championship dimmed, another
awaited. By Joe Lapointe.
</P>
<P>
   SOC-WORLDCUP-NYT (Marseille, France) _ World cup host team
impressive in 3-0 win over South Africa. By Christopher Clarey.
</P>
<P>
   RAC-COMEBACK-NYT (Undated) _ Silver Charm returns to action. By
Joseph Durso.
</P>
<P>
   BKN-ARATON-COLUMN (Chicago) _ It's as much Pippen's fight as
Jordan's. By Harvey Araton.
</P>
<P>
   SOC-VECSEY-COLUMN (Paris) _ In Germany, playing soccer is all
business. By George Vecsey.
</P>
<P>
   OUTDOORS-WOMEN-FISHING (Undated) _ Women bridging gap as Keys
fishing guides. By Nicholas Karas.
</P>
