<P>
   GENERAL
</P>
<P>
   KASHMIR/Territory, Controversy -- 3X8 1/2 --
</P>
<P>
   (BC-KASHMIR-CONTROVERSY-NYT) Kashmir at a glance; India's and
Pakistan's
</P>
<P>
   claims to the territory.
</P>
