<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1998-06-13 22:04 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A8065 &Cx1f; ttc-z
r s &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-BBN-MODESTI-LADN     06-13 0944
