</P>
<P>
   A7885 BC-EXP-RACE-CATEGORIES-NYT 352 16:09 U A
</P>
<P>
   U.S. OFFICIALS STRUGGLE WITH MULTIRACIAL HERITAGE
</P>
<P>
   A7883 BC-EXP-BAPTISTS-MORMONS-NYT 364 16:06 U A
</P>
<P>
   BAPTISTS TAKE THEIR MESSAGE INTO MORMON TERRITORY
</P>
<P>
   A7878 BC-EXP-CALIF-BILINGUAL-FOE-NYT 399 15:54 U A
</P>
<P>
   THE IDEOLOGUE WHO `FIXED' BILINGUAL EDUCATION
</P>
<P>
   A7876 BC-CLINTON-SCHOOL-KILLINGS-NYT 653 15:52 U A
